    "Enhancement TechniquesThis section focuses on the supplementary systems within the unified framework (Fig. 4), as illustrated in Fig.",
    "We systematically review key techniques across three phases of pre-generation, post-generation, and system-level synergy, revealing how they mitigate the inherent deficiencies of LLMs in structural understanding and quality assurance by integrating established software engineering methodologies.While advanced prompt engineering significantly enhances the generation capabilities of Large Language Models (LLMs), LLMs remain probabilistic models with no intrinsic understanding of code structure, execution semantics, or test quality.",
    "To address this fundamental limitation, researchers integrate LLMs with a spectrum of established software engineering techniques.",
